current_contact.agency: New Mexico State Med Inv Ofc

case_circumstances: A father and son were going to fish at the irrigation canal just west of 2nd street. They went down to the water and noted something floating in the water and was lodged against a log. The father took a closer look and found it to be a body. They then left and called the PD. The decedent was in the water and lodged up against a log and decomposed. There were no obvious signs of trauma noted. No ID was found on the decedent. It is unknown how the decedent ended up in the water and where he went into or was dumped in to the water.
